c: 10
v: 18
t: "Mpe bazali kobondela basusu baye bakoki kosala bango mabe to malamu te, batiki Allah, mpe bazali koloba: Ba oyo nde bakolobelela biso epai ya Allah. Loba: Bolingi koloba ete Allah ayebi te maye mazali o likolo na mabele? Lokumu naye Nkolo wa likolo na maye bazali kosangisa ye na yango"